Show HN: ML-Powered Search Demo
text:
Before NLP-powered text search, it was difficult to handle synonyms or text records with different languages. This demo is a note-taking app that can accommodate 16 languages for semantic search that makes searching through your content way better than substrings.

Please feel free to ask any questions and leave comments about your impressions. There is no CSS - it's intentional. Function over form :)

Ask HN: Job Opportunities for FACS Coders?
text:
Undoubtedly, an average person knowing how to interpret facial expressions and, more broadly, body language and emotions could benefit in many ways in their daily life. However, I am specifically wondering about job opportunities for people intimately familiar with the FACS [0] - whether in tech or beyond. What kind of companies, agencies, or institutions hire these people? What are the possible salary ranges?

[0]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Facial_Action_Coding_System
